    "content_cards_9beXWQ": {
      "type": "content-cards",
      "blocks": {
        "card_GdHCyF": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "show_number": true,
            "number": "1. The Harvest",
            "show_icon": true,
            "show_text": true,
            "text": "<p>Each botanical is handpicked at the precise moment when its aromatic and active compounds are at their peak. We follow the natural cycles of the plant, its growth, flowering, and rest, rather than imposing fixed schedules.</p>"
          }
        },
        "card_VigfAF": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "show_number": true,
            "number": "2. Extraction",
            "show_icon": true,
            "show_text": true,
            "text": "<p>The botanicals are placed into our alembic for steam distillation. Water is boiled at the base, creating steam that rises through the plant material, releasing its aromatic compounds. As the steam cools it separates into the essential oil and the hydrolat<em>.</em></p>"
          }
        },
        "card_Ha7apU": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "show_number": true,
            "number": "3. Maturation",
            "show_icon": true,
            "show_text": true,
            "text": "<p>Freshly distilled oils are vibrant but often incomplete. With time, they soften, deepen and become balanced. We allow our essential oils to mature under controlled conditions, allowing notes to integrate naturally. The result is a richer, more harmonious olfactory profile.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "card_GdHCyF",
        "card_VigfAF",
        "card_Ha7apU"
      ],
      "name": "Content cards",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Extracting the botanicals",
        "description": "<p>In The Lab our Scent Scientists go to great lengths to harvest and preserve the precious botanicals from our farm.</p>",
        "section_width": "page-width",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "padding-block-start": 80,
        "padding-block-end": 0
      }
    },
    "content_cards_CrJNJA": {
      "type": "content-cards",
      "blocks": {
        "card_qHRQtd": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "show_number": true,
            "number": "4. The Organ",
            "show_icon": true,
            "show_text": true,
            "text": "<p>The organ is the creative heart of our laboratory. Here, natural raw materials, essential oils, resins and extracts are arranged with precision as compositions are built note by note. It is a place of refinement, where each formula evolves through careful adjustment until it finds its balance.</p>"
          }
        },
        "card_tiKjxA": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "show_number": true,
            "number": "5. The Final Blend",
            "show_icon": true,
            "show_text": true,
            "text": "<p>Through repeated iterations of each formula, we refine each blend until it expresses a clear identity, one that feels both coherent and deeply connected to its origin. It is the final blend that will tell the unique sensory story.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "card_qHRQtd",
        "card_tiKjxA"
      ],
      "name": "Content cards",
