                    "text": "<p>The Cala Falcó Collection is crafted using premium natural ingredients, such as essential oils, botanical extracts, and Mediterranean herbs. You’ll find ingredients like lavender, rosemary, mastic and citrus fruits, all selected for their mood-enhancing and skin-nourishing properties​.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_eCzNhx"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_3N9xkP": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "How can using Cala Falcó Collection impact my mood?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_cLHenE": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Our collections are designed to influence emotions and mental states through aromachology. By using ingredients known for their calming, energising, or balancing effects, such as rockrose, bergamot, and mint, our perfumes, diffusers, and candles help you create an atmosphere that suits your mood.​</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_cLHenE"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_Jq4pHM": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What makes the Cala Falcó Collection sustainable?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_hKRV6w": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "t:names.text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>We focus on sustainable sourcing for our natural ingredients, ensuring that our products are both luxurious and environmentally conscious. Our eco-friendly packaging and commitment to biodegradable surfactants reflect our dedication to minimising environmental impact​. Read more about our sustainability programme here.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_hKRV6w"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_WPQEJD": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Are all the products in the collection  handcrafted?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_GBkqzg": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "t:names.text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Yes, each product is meticulously handcrafted in small batches. Even the botanicals we use are mostly hand picked. This artisanal approach ensures that every fragrance, cosmetic, and diffuser is made with care and precision, resulting in a unique, high-quality experience​.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
